name: QICoreEncounterTypeSCT
title: QICore Encounter Type SCT
description: Addresses US Core 5.0.1 not covering many codes used in CMS eCQMs
purpose:
(Clinical Focus: Encounter types),(Data Element Scope: FHIR Encounter.type or QDM Encounter, Performed.code),(Inclusion Criteria: Used on CMS Annual Update eCQMs, SNOMED only
also includes US Core 5.0.1 Encounter Type value set SCT codes),(Exclusion Criteria: may consider excluding US Core codes then adding them back in a Grouping value set)
